      {
        "title": "Guardian",
        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Cover Ally                  Novice                                                              You cover your ally with a shield, protecting them from attacks                                               Implacable Mark                  Novice                                                              You foil enemy attacks by menacing your foes                                               Polearm Master                  Novice                                                              You hit any creature that enters your reach                                               Pushing Strike                  Novice                                                              You reposition your enemies as you hit them with attacks                                               Sentinel                  Novice                                                              You occupy your enemies’ attention, protecting nearby allies                                               Stand and Fight                  Novice                                                              You stop creatures from running away from you                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Cover Ally                              Novice                                             Duration           Until the start of your next turn                                  Choose an ally you can see. Attacks against your ally have disadvantage while you are wielding a shield and your ally is adjacent to you.                                  Implacable Mark                              Novice                        Make a melee Strike. If you hit, the target is marked until the end of your next turn. A marked target has disadvantage on any attack against a creature other than you.                                  Polearm Master                              Novice                                             Trigger           A creature enters your reach                                  Make a melee Strike with a polearm or spear against the triggering creature.                                  Pushing Strike                              Novice                        Make a melee Strike with a club, polearm, shield, or spear. If you hit, you can push your target up to 5 feet in a direction of your choice.                                  Sentinel                              Novice                                             Trigger           A creature you can reach attacks a target other than you                                  Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature.                                  Stand and Fight                              Novice                                             Trigger           A creature you can reach uses a Move power                                  Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature. If you hit, you cancel your target’s power, and your target can’t use Move powers for the rest of its turn.",
        "url": "/guardian.html"
      }
      
