      {
        "title": "Inventor",
        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Automatic Ballista                  Novice                                                              Summon a turret that lasts for 1 minute                                               Magitech Engine                  Novice                                                              Craft a small engine with an elemental effect                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Automatic Ballista                              Novice                                       Manipulate                                                      Duration           10 minutes                                  You set up an automatic turret on a flat surface you can reach. The turret is a creature with 10 * your Inventor level HP, 15 AC, 0 Speed, and the Minion trait. The turret can fire its cannon as a ranged Strike. This deals 2d8 damage, uses your Crafting score as the Weapon Skill, and has a range of 120 feet.                                  Magitech Engine                              Novice                                       Manipulate                                                      Duration           1 minute after the engine is attached to a weapon, or 1 hour otherwise                                  You craft a small magic device that outputs a stream of elemental energy. Choose the engine’s element to be one of acid, electricity, ice, fire, magic, or sound. With 1 minute of work, you can set up the engine to perform a single minor effect related to its element, at the GM’s discretion.   When you craft the engine, or as an  power after you craft the engine, you can attach it to a weapon you touch. Strikes with that weapon deal an extra 1d6 damage. A weapon can only have one engine attached to it at a time.",
        "url": "/inventor.html"
      }
      
