      {
        "title": "Mastermind",
        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              Chessmaster                  Novice                                                              Reveal you planned this all along! (change the plot)                                               Inspiring Speech                  Novice                                                              Increase allies’ AC and damage for 1 minute                                               Order                  Novice                                                              An ally acts instead of you                                               Knight's Move                  Veteran                                                              Let an ally move instead of you                                               White Raven Tactics                  Veteran                                                              Let an ally take an extra turn                                               Dirge of Doom                  Novice                                                                                                             Dispiriting Taunt                  Novice                                                                                                             Inspire Courage                  Novice                                                                                                             Inspire Heroics                  Veteran                                                                                     Unity                  Veteran                                                                                                             Soothing Ballad                  Master                                                                                                             Fatal Performance                  Epic                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 Chessmaster                              Novice                                       Daily                                 You announce that you planned this all along! You explain the details of your plan, which retroactively become fact. You cannot change any established events in the story, and your plan must be something that you could have reasonably prepared within the past 24 hours. Your plan cannot involve any actions that would require die rolls to succeed.   For example, if you are investigating a dungeon, you could announce that you remembered to bring 100 feet of rope and a grappling hook, as you had anticipated that you might fall down a chasm. Alternatively, if you are in a meeting with the evil mayor, you could announce that you had arranged for the captain of the guard to be wandering by at just the right time, as you had predicted that the mayor would reveal his plan as this exact time. The GM has final say on whether any plan is reasonable.                                  Inspiring Speech                              Novice                                       Auditory                    Linguistic                                                      Area           30-foot emanation                    Duration           1 minute                                  Your target’s AC increases by 2, and whenever they deal damage with an Attack, then can add 1d8 to the damage against one target                                  Order                              Novice                                       Auditory                    Linguistic                                                      Range           30 feet                    Requirements           Your target hasn’t been affected by Order in the past minute                                  You shout a brief order that spurs your ally into action. The target can immediately use a  power.                                  Knight's Move                              Veteran                                       Auditory                    Linguistic                                                      Range           60 feet                    Requirements           You haven’t used the Stride power yet this turn                                  Your target can immediately use the Stride power. You can’t use the Stride power for the rest of your turn.                                  White Raven Tactics                              Veteran                                       Auditory                    Daily                    Linguistic                                                      Range           30 feet                                  Your target immediately takes an extra turn outside of the normal initiative order.                                  Dirge of Doom                              Novice                                       Composition                    Emotion                    Fear                    Mental                                                      Area           30-foot emanation                    Duration           1 round                                  Foes within the area are frightened 1. They can’t reduce their frightened value below 1 while they remain in the area.                                  Dispiriting Taunt                              Novice                                       Auditory                    Emotion                    Fear                    Linguistic                    Mental                                                      Range           60 feet                    Duration           1 round                                  Make an Intimidate roll against the target’s Will DC.                                   Critical Success           As success, and the target is stunned 1                             Success           The target has a -2 penalty to all die rolls                             Failure           The target has a -2 penalty to attack rolls                                                        Inspire Courage                              Novice                                       Composition                    Emotion                    Mental                                                      Area           60-foot emanation                    Duration           1 round                                  You inspire your allies with words or tunes of encouragement. You and all allies in the area gain one of the following benefits:     +1 bonus to attack rolls, damage rolls, and saves against Fear effects   +1 bonus to AC and saving throws, as well as resistance to physical damage equal to your Envoy level   +10-foot bonus to Speed                                  Inspire Heroics              Veteran                                             Prerequisites           Inspire Courage                                  The bonuses granted by Inspire Courage are doubled.                                  Unity                              Veteran                                       Fortune                                                      Trigger           You and 1 or more allies within range are targeted by a spell or ability that allows a saving throw                    Range           30 feet                    Targets           Each ally targeted by the triggering spell                                  You put up a united defense. Each ally can use your saving throw modifier instead of its own against the triggering spell. Each ally decides individually which modifier to use.                                  Soothing Ballad                              Master                                       Composition                    Emotion                    Healing                    Mental                                                      Range           30 feet                    Targets           You and up to 9 allies                                  You draw upon your muse to soothe your allies. Choose one of the following three effects:     Disrupt all Fear effects on the targets   Disrupt all effects causing the paralyzed condition on the targets   Restore 7d8 HP to the targets                                  Fatal Performance                              Epic                                       Composition                    Death                    Emotion                    Encounter                    Mental                                                      Range           30 feet                                  Your performance is so perfect that the target may die of joy or sorrow. The target takes 50 damage. If this brings it to 0 HP, it dies instantly.",
        "url": "/mastermind.html"
      }
      
