      {
        "title": "Blaster",
        "excerpt": "Powers          Name     Tier     Type     Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      Acid Arrow                  Novice                                                                                                             Bolt                  Novice                                                                                                             Dangerous Sorcery                  Novice                                                                                     Magic Missile                  Novice                                                                                                             Sound Burst                  Novice                                                                                                             Spell Shaper                  Veteran                                                                                     Cone of Cold                  Veteran                                                                                                             Fireball                  Veteran                                                                                                             Lightning Bolt                  Veteran                                                                                                             Chain Lightning                  Master                                                                                                             Disintegrate                  Master                                                                                                             Polar Ray                  Master                                                                                                             Implosion                  Epic                                                                                                             Meteor Swarm                  Epic                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Acid Arrow                              Novice                                       Acid                    Attack                    Spell                                                      Cost           2 Mana                    Range           120 feet                                  You conjure an arrow of acid that continues corroding the target after it hits. Make a spell attack against the target. On a hit, you deal 3d8 acid damage plus 1d6 persistent acid damage. On a critical hit, double the initial damage, but not the persistent damage.      Heightened (per +2 Mana)   The intial damage increases by 2d8, and the persistant acid damage increases by 1d6                                  Bolt                              Novice                                       Attack                    Cantrip                    Spell                                                      Range           60 feet                                  You fire a bolt of damaging magical energies that impacts with violent force. Make a Magic attack roll against the target’s defense.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 1d6                                            Success           You deal 1d6 + Magic damage                                                                 Dangerous Sorcery              Novice                        Your arcane knowledge grants you great destructive power. When you cast a spell, if the spell deals damage and doesn’t have a duration, you gain a bonus to that spell’s damage equal to your Blaster level.                                  Magic Missile                              Novice                                       Force                    Spell                                                      Cost           1 Mana                    Range           30 feet                                  You fire an unerring dart of force from your fingertips. It automatically hits and deals 1d4+1 force damage to the target.                                  Sound Burst                              Novice                                       Spell                    Sonic                                                      Cost           2 Mana                    Range           30 feet                    Area           10-foot burst                    Save           Fortitude                                  A cacophonous noise blasts out, dealing 2d10 sonic damage. Each creature must attempt a Fortitude save.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 1d10                                   Critical Success           The creature is unaffected                             Success           The creature takes half damage                             Failure           The creature takes full damage and is deafened for 1 round                             Critical Failure           The creature takes double damage and is deafened and slowed 1 for 1 minute                                               Spell Shaper              Veteran                        When you use a Blaster Attack power with a range of at least 30 feet, you can decrease the range to Touch to get a +2 bonus to the attack roll.                                  Cone of Cold                              Veteran                                       Cold                    Spell                                                      Cost           5 Mana                    Area           60-foot cone                    Save           Reflex                                  Icy cold rushes forth from your hands. You deal 12d6 cold damage to creatures in the area.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 2d6                                  Fireball                              Veteran                                       Fire                    Spell                                                      Cost           3 Mana                    Range           500 feet                    Area           20-foot burst                    Save           Reflex                                  A roaring blast of fire appears at a spot you designate, dealing 6d6 fire damage.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 2d6                                  Lightning Bolt                              Veteran                                       Electricity                    Spell                                                      Cost           3 Mana                    Area           120-foot line                    Save           Reflex                                  A bolt of lightning strikes outward from your hand, dealing 4d12 electricity damage.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 1d12                                  Chain Lightning                              Master                                       Electricity                    Spell                                                      Cost           6 Mana                    Range           30 feet                    Save           Reflex                                  You discharge a powerful bolt of lightning at the target, dealing 8d12 electricity damage. The target must attempt a Reflex save. The electricity arcs to another creature within 30 feet of the first target, jumps to another creature within 30 feet of that target, and so on. You can end the chain at any point. You can’t target the same creature more than once, and you must be able to see all targets. Roll the damage only once, and apply it to each target. The chain ends if any target critical succeeds at its save.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 1d12                                  Disintegrate                              Master                                       Attack                    Spell                                                      Cost           6 Mana                    Range           120 feet                                  You fire a green ray at your target. Make a spell attack. If you hit, you deal 12d10 damage, or twice as much on a critical hit. A creature reduced to 0 HP is reduced to fine powder. An object you hit is destroyed if it would fit within a 10-foot cube, regardless of its HP, unless it’s an artifact or similarly hard to destroy.                                  Polar Ray                              Master                                       Attack                    Cold                    Spell                                                      Cost           8 Mana                    Range           120 feet                                  You fire a blue-white ray of freezing air and swirling sleet from your finger that can chill your target to the bones. You must succeed at a spell attack roll to affect the target, which then takes 10d8 damage and is drained 2.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The damage increases by 2d8                                  Implosion                              Epic                                       Spell                                                      Cost           9 Mana                    Range           30 feet                    Save           Fortitude                    Duration           Sustained, up to 1 minute                                  You crush the target by causing it to collapse in on itself, dealing 75 damage. Each time you Sustain the spell, you must choose a new target to be subject to the same effect. You can’t target the same creature twice during a single casting of this spell, you can’t Sustain this spell multiple times per turn, and you can’t target a creature that lacks a solid form.                                  Meteor Swarm                              Epic                                       Spell                                                      Cost           9 Mana                    Range           500 feet                    Save           Reflex                                  You call down four meteors that explode in fiery blasts. Each meteor deals 6d10 bludgeoning damage to all creatures in a 10-foot burst, then explodes, dealing 14d6 fire damage to all creatures in a 40-foot burst. A creature hit by multiple meteors takes damage only once.      Heightened (per +1 Mana)   The bludgeoning damage increases by 1d10, and the fire damage increases by 2d6",
        "url": "/blaster.html"
      }
      
